{"tid":294181,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"(驚世新政)中超禁止球迷攜帶專業相機進入觀眾看台","createTime":"2017-06-22T17:45:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-23T09:11:20.000Z","uid":37218,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"118b889b248283cf904bb224d7e14dcec5f1b659","tid":294181,"uid":37218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T17:45:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/qxf0i1c5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fqxf0i1c5&h=4c0f39ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n足協通知:禁止攜帶專業相機進入中超觀眾看台<br />\n<br />\n日期:6月21日，中國足協發佈職業聯賽理事會執行局的通知內容，禁止觀眾攜帶專業相機進入中超聯賽觀眾看台區域。<br />\n<br />\n　　通知內容：為了更好地維護中超聯賽賽場秩序，打造安全有序的觀賽環境，自2017中國平安中超聯賽第十四輪起，嚴禁入場觀眾攜帶200mm（含）以上長鏡頭、角架及重量超過500克的機身進入中超聯賽觀眾看台區域。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"403d560fa8e82b8571bf268c270687fde49a154d","tid":294181,"uid":31,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T17:57:10.000Z","msg":"原因？"},{"pid":"ca0ba6e541870237405658f6633a54780a29a74a","tid":294181,"uid":37218,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T18:04:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原因？</blockquote><br />\n聲稱為咗賽場秩序，但內面都係因為金錢利益問題"},{"pid":"b49b3be4cf0d522e03e47bc74e3dcae3624dda1c","tid":294181,"uid":97997,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T19:13:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>原因？</blockquote><br />\n聲稱為咗賽場秩序，但內面都係因為金錢利益問題</blockquote><br />\n有咩金錢利益可言，唔通喺球場開live咩<br />\n中超班管理層冇腦，見佢哋又外援限制，又轉會費限制，又咩u21<br />\n咁多錢請教練教國家隊，冇錢請啲外國做管理嘅人，搵唔識足球嘅人管理咪就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"249b51f3f398dc53e4